{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_08_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 中身だけなくなってる",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年末の、ある日のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day at the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん\n今日は、事務所の大掃除をするんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.\nToday's the day we're cleaning the office‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。休みなのに、手伝いに来てもらって悪いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Sorry to ask you to come help out on your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.000000012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私達も、いつもこの事務所を使ってるんですから\n綺麗にするのは当たり前のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We always use this office too‚\nso it’s only natural that we help clean it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺と橋本さんだけじゃ絶対に終わらないから、助かるよ\n……ところで、そこの大荷物は一体なんなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would never get done with just me and Hashimoto-san‚ so it really helps.\n…By the way‚ what's with that huge pile of stuff?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "事務所の大掃除をするにあたって\n動画サイトで、お掃除の動画をいくつか観てみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In preparation for cleaning the office‚\nI watched some cleaning videos online.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "プロ用の専用洗剤の威力に、隙間の埃を取るコツ……\n重曹がああも万能とは思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The power of specialized professional detergents‚ the tips for removing dust from crevices…\nI never realized baking soda was so versatile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "後はもう実践するのみと思って、紹介されていた洗剤や\nスポンジを買ってきたんです。そうだ、他にも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I thought practice was all I needed‚ so I bought the cleaning agents and\nsponges that they recommended. Oh‚ and there’s also――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、沙季、気合いは十分伝わってきたから\nそろそろ始めようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sa-Saki‚ I can definitely feel your enthusiasm‚\nso shall we get started?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5855272822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、続きは実践で、ということですね\nでは、早速大掃除を始めましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. You mean I should learn the rest through practice‚ right?\nThen let’s start cleaning right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "私は冷蔵庫の中を整理しますね\n賞味期限切れの物が、入ったままになっていたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll organize the inside of the refrigerator.\nSome things are past their expiration dates.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "それから……{user}さんは\nまず、ご自分の机の整理整頓をお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… {user}-san‚\nplease start by organizing your desk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "部屋の乱れは心の乱れですよ\nいい仕事をするためには、まず環境を綺麗に整えないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A cluttered room reflects a cluttered mind.\nTo do good work‚ you need to start by cleaning up your surroundings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "き、肝に銘じておきます……\nはぁ……我ながら、これは骨が折れそうだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'll keep that in mind…\nUgh… This is going to be a pain…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "冷蔵庫は整理したし、次はこっちの本棚を……\nああ、やっぱり。雑誌の並びがバラバラになってますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I finished organizing the refrigerator‚ now it’s time for the bookshelf…\nAh‚ as I thought. The magazines are all out of order.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと刊行順に並べ直さないと\n……ええと、ここまでが2020年。こっちが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to rearrange them in order of publication.\nLet’s see… This is up to 2020. And this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1984422084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……さ、沙季？　おーい……\nそこまで細かくやってたら、今年中に終わらないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sa-Saki? Hello…?\nIf you keep being so meticulous‚ we’ll never finish this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。午後には皆も手伝いに来てくれますし\nこのオフィスの整理を10時45分までに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's alright. Everyone will come to help in the afternoon‚\nand if we finish organizing this office by 10:45‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "エントランスの掃除を11時30分までに終えれば\n今日の夕方には、事務所を掃除し終わる予定ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and cleaning the entrance by 11:30‚\nwe’ll be done cleaning the office by this evening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで分刻みのスケジュールでやるのか！？\nま、まぁ、沙季らしいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re going to clean on such a minute-by-minute schedule?!\nWell‚ well‚ that sounds like you‚ Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8333300273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの進捗はどうですか？\n机の整頓の終了予定時刻まで、後五分ですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How’s your progress going‚ {user}-san?\nThere are only five minutes left until the scheduled completion time for your desk organization.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、急いで終わらせてきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'll finish it quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6333264788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？\nこの箱、中身だけなくなってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh?\nThis box… the contents are gone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "ない、確かにこの桐箱に入れて棚に置いておいたのに\nどうしよう、大事な物だったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's empty… I’m sure I put it in this wooden box and left it on the shelf…\nWhat should I do? It was important…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "大事な物……？\n俺も一緒に探すよ、その箱に何を入れてたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An important thing…?\nI will help you to find it‚ what did you put in the box?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.9333300273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "御朱印帳です\n赤い布張りの表紙で、大きさはこのくらいの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s my *goshuincho. （*Shrine stamp book）\nIt had a red cloth cover‚ and it was about this big…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.2999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それなら俺も覚えてる\nしばらく前の神社のロケで、沙季がもらったやつだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I remember it‚ too.\nIt’s the one you got during the shrine shoot a while back‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.6999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "そう、それです！　私達が、NEXT VENUS\nグランプリで優勝したばかりの頃に――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that’s it! Right after we won\nthe NEXT VENUS Grand Prix――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.6999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ決勝から間もなく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Shortly after the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.1000145079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.3333488585
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.4333458067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
